description: Vanoil Energy Ltd. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of crude oil and natural gas properties in Kenya and the Seychelles. The company holds 100% interests in two onshore blocks, 3A and 3B, totaling 24,912 square kilometers in Eastern Kenya. It also holds 25% interests in Areas A and B that cover 14,319 square kilometers located in Seychelles. Vanoil Energy Ltd. was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
